data.title: A remembrance ceremony of His Majesty the late King Bhumibol Adulyadej’s Birthday Anniversary 5 December 2023
data.meta_description: A remembrance ceremony of His Majesty the late King Bhumibol Adulyadej’s Birthday Anniversary 5 December 2023
data.meta_site_name: สถานเอกอัครราชทูต ณ กรุงมานามา
data.text: On 3 December 2023, H.E. Ambassador Piyapak Sricharoen presided over a remembrance ceremony of His Majesty the late King Bhumibol Adulyadej’s Birthday Anniversary 5 December 2023, with the Embassy’s diplomatic staff, their spouses, and Royal Thai Navy representatives participating.
